property.description:
Lakeshore Cabin at Big Bear Lake | Hot Tub | Pool Table | Boat Dock&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Lake Shore, a stunning lakeside retreat nestled in the heart of Big Bear Lake. This charming home offers a perfect blend of comfort and adventure, making it an ideal getaway for families and friends alike. With breathtaking lake views and direct access to the water, you can immerse yourself in the beauty of nature right from your doorstep.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This spacious home features three beautifully appointed bedrooms and three bathrooms, accommodating up to eight guests. The main level boasts two luxurious king bedrooms, each with its own private bath, ensuring a restful night&amp;#39;s sleep. A separate guest apartment downstairs includes a cozy queen bed and a bunk bed, perfect for kids or additional guests.&amp;nbsp;The ambiance of Lake Shore is warm and inviting, with a well-designed living area that includes a fireplace and a smart TV for your entertainment. The fully equipped kitchen is a chef&amp;#39;s dream, featuring modern appliances, a dining area, and all the essentials needed to prepare delicious meals. Enjoy your culinary creations on the private balcony or decked area, where you can soak in the stunning views while dining al fresco. Step outside to discover a private yard, complete with outdoor seating and a BBQ grill, perfect for summer cookouts. The property also offers access to a communal pool and hot tub, providing a refreshing escape during warmer months.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
For those seeking adventure, the surrounding area is rich with activities such as hiking, skiing, and water sports, ensuring there&amp;#39;s something for everyone. Safety and comfort are prioritized with features like a carbon monoxide detector, smoke detector, and central heating. The property is pet-friendly, allowing you to bring your furry friends along for the fun. With free Wi-Fi and a game room equipped with a pool table and air hockey, you&amp;#39;ll have everything you need for a memorable stay. Located just a short walk from local shops, dining, and marinas, 012-Lake Shore is the perfect base for exploring all that Big Bear Lake has to offer. Don&amp;#39;t miss out on this incredible opportunity to create lasting memories in a beautiful setting. Book your stay today and experience the magic of lakeside living!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: King Bed, Streaming TV, Private Bath w/ Jetted Spa Tub- Entry Upper Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: King Bed, Private 3/4 Bath- Entry Upper Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3 | Guest Apartment: Queen/Queen Bunk + Queen Bed, Streaming TV, 3/4 Bath- Lower/Separate Bottom Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Private Full Bath w/ Jetted Spa Tub- Bedroom 1- Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Private 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)- Bedroom 2- Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)- Bedroom 3- Separate Guest Apartment- Lower Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
-Sleeps 8&lt;br /&gt;
-3 Car Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
-3 Pets Welcome w/ Additional Fees&lt;br /&gt;
-1,511 Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
City Permit #: VRR-2025-0002

