property.description:
Breezy One Lakeside Family Cabin at Big Bear&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Breezy One- this is the perfect lakeside retreat for a group of friends, family reunion, or couple&amp;#39;s retreat to the mountains boasting all that you need for a memorable and relaxing trip no matter the season you choose to visit. Sitting just a mile from the Big Bear Village and local marinas you have the very best of Big Bear right at your fingertips from this spacious two story chalet. Boasting the necessities from home along with cooking and dining essentials you will have a spacious lakeside yard including a nice patio area, seasonal boat dock, and BBQ area for your enjoyment- the possibilities are endless from here.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter into a cozy and warm living room area where you can snuggle up on the leather sofas and warm your toes together in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace as you enjoy your lakeside location and amazing views. Enjoy a movie night in at your cabin on the flat screen TV with Cable and complimentary hi speed WIFI internet supplied for you by the owners. Around the corner you will find the equipped kitchen and dining areas complete with all that the chef of your group will need to whip up your home cooked meals or holidays feasts right here at the cabin- oak cabinets pair with counter space and cookware plus appliances and a dishwasher to ensure that your cleanup is a breeze. A separate laundry room area offers your group a washer and dryer on hand for those wet snow clothes or extended visits here in the mountains as an added convenience.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This spacious retreat offers four comfortable sleeping areas and plenty of bathrooms for a comfortable group vacation, all of which are made up for your group with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive. Outside the beautiful property offers patio seating and a picnic table where your group can enjoy your time here together in the mountains as you grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake on the Charcoal BBQ. The summer months are the absolute best here at Breezy Cabin with a lakeside location offering a seasonal boat dock for your lake activities and toys all while located within a short stroll to local marinas and the Village shops for dining and entertainment. This home is the larger of two properties that share this location, both are available to rent separately or together for even more family or friends to join in the adventure.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
