&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Breezy Estate!! Perfect for a family vacation, group of friends, corporate retreat, or just a come together of any kind this fabulous property consists of a combination of two furnished lakeside cabins next to each other in a quiet Mallard Bay location which is an awesome destination, providing all that you need for a large group or multi-family vacation to the mountains. Furnished with the essentials and necessities for a memorable trip you will love this location which is especially awesome in the summer months with a seasonal boat dock available for your lake activities.&lt;br /&gt;
