&lt;br /&gt;
Frank&amp;#39;s Old Bear is a nicely remodeled and fully furnished single story family cabin that sits on a gorgeous, treed lot right on the shores of Big Bear Lake, with community boat dock access, a fenced back yard and within a short walk to the downtown Village or local marinas for lake activities, this is the perfect destination for any mountain vacation! You will absolutely love the amazing front deck with an gorgeous views of the lake and surroundings, newer patio furniture, and a piped Natural BBQ for your use during your stay.&lt;br /&gt;
