&lt;br /&gt;
Looking to experience the ultimate Big Bear vacation right from the shoreline!? Cove Lakefront Chalet is the perfect vacation home for just that! Sitting on the shoreline in the quiet Boulder Bay neighborhood of the valley, your group will have an abundance of activities right at your fingertips while still within a ten-minute car ride to the ski resorts or downtown Village shops. Sprawling in fully furnished spaces for your group to enjoy our two-story home has all that you need for a memorable visit to the mountains including entertaining games, kitchen essentials, and a new private hot tub under the stars!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter into a grand living room area upon entry with vaulted knotty pine cathedral ceilings and soaring picture windows to take in the panoramic lake views surrounding you. Comfortable sitting couches offer great spaces to sit and make memories around a toasty rock wood-burning fireplace. Enjoy your favorite movie on the massive flat-screen Streaming TV or just snuggle up and watch the snow falling outside. (Guests must have their own accounts to use Streaming services.) There are two separate lake view dining areas that each offer a custom formal log dining table for your group or holiday meals together along with deck access and more fantastic lake views. The breakfast bar pairs stool seats and gorgeous granite countertops for your chef to prepare your home-cooked meals. The oak cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils for your convenience while general appliances and a dishwasher ensure that your meals are a breeze here!&lt;br /&gt;
