&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Lakeview Getaway, where the charm of a furnished family lake house meets the comfort of a mountain escape cabin, creating the perfect setting for a memorable vacation with friends or family in Big Bear. Nestled in a quiet and serene cove, this cozy retreat offers year-round beauty and convenience, keeping you just a short stroll away from local marinas and the downtown Village. A quick drive will get you to grocery stores or ski resorts in under ten minutes. Plus, enjoy the seasonal boat dock for summer lake adventures! (Water Levels Pending - Photo is May 2023)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step into the warm and inviting family room, where rustic mountain charm envelops you. Original wood walls and ceilings, a toasty brick fireplace, and stunning open windows offer wonderful lake views. Snuggle up on the comfy couches, warm your toes by the wood-burning fireplace, and enjoy a movie on the flat-screen Streaming TV with complimentary high-speed WiFi provided by the owner. (Guests must have their own accounts to access Streaming Services.)&lt;br /&gt;
