Private 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)- Bedroom 1- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Private 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)- In Den- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
-Sleeps 12 Max&amp;nbsp;| 8 Adults &amp;amp; 4 Children&lt;br /&gt;
-3 Cars Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
-NO PETS ALLOWED- Fines Imposed For Pets Found On Premises&lt;br /&gt;
