property.description:
&lt;div&gt;Serenity Cove Lake House- Incredible Waterfront Oasis Retreat&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Serenity Cove&amp;mdash;where luxury meets family adventure in a secluded, fun-filled retreat at Big Bear Lake&amp;rsquo;s prestigious Gilner Point. Serenity Cove is a stunning waterfront haven that blends elegance with relaxation, offering breathtaking views and an unmatched sense of privacy. Escape the city and immerse yourself in nature&amp;rsquo;s beauty, from the majestic mountains to the serene lakeside. Your experience begins with our private dock, perfect for boating, fishing, kayaking, and paddleboarding. For those who love the outdoors, nearby hiking trails provide panoramic vistas, ideal for capturing great photos.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Inside, discover a world of comfort and excitement. The expansive game room is perfect for family fun, with board games, movies, and a loft space that&amp;rsquo;s a dream for kids or anyone young at heart. Our three king bedrooms and two and a half baths offer plenty of room for everyone, while the large, fully equipped kitchen invites culinary creativity&amp;mdash;ideal for family feasts or group meals. Step out onto the extended deck for a barbecue or unwind in the hot tub under a canopy of stars. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re soaking in the eight-person spa or enjoying the cozy warmth of one of the three wood-burning fireplaces, your cabin&amp;nbsp;offers the&amp;nbsp;perfect blend of relaxation and excitement.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This isn&amp;rsquo;t just a luxurious escape; it&amp;rsquo;s also packed with modern conveniences including smart home features like a Google Home thermostat, a Bose speaker with an Apple adapter, and an EV charger port, every detail is designed with excellence in mind. Ample driveway parking ensures that your cars and trailers are accommodated with ease. This family-friendly oasis is surrounded by lush landscaping, creating a tranquil and charming setting. Around the corner from Holloway&amp;rsquo;s Marina and countless opportunities for adventure, Serenity Cove is more than just a home&amp;mdash;it&amp;rsquo;s an unforgettable escape where lifelong memories are made.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: King Bed, Lake Views, Deck Access, Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: King Bed, Lake Views, Streaming TV, Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3: King Bed, Streaming TV, Fireplace, Lake Views, Balcony, Deck Access, Private Bath- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Game Room | Loft: Two Twin Beds + Full Sleeper Sofa, Game Table, Streaming TV, Fireplace, Private Balcony - Upstairs 3rd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Private 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)- Bedroom 3- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Private Half Bath- Game Room Loft- Upstairs 3rd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
-Sleeps 10&lt;br /&gt;
-4 Car Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
-NO PETS ALLOWED- Fines Imposed for Pets Found on Property&lt;br /&gt;
-2,274 Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
City Permit #: VRR-2025-0438

