Bear Lake Lodge Lakefront | Incredible Lake House Chalet&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Bear Lake Lodge! This centrally located Eagle Point lakefront chalet is custom built from the ground up with your vacation stay in mind. Boasting spectacular lake views from every room and an incredible floor plan, this home provides plenty of room for families, friends, corporate retreats, and entertaining within an incredible lakefront setting. Sitting within minutes to the slopes, Village shops, and local Big Bear marinas, you have the best of Big Bear right at your fingertips from here!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Including three levels of comfortable living space, your group has convenient access to 5 spacious bedrooms, 6 modern bathrooms, a fun packed game room, plus a gourmet kitchen and formal dining area- there is an abundance of space to spend time making memories with your loved ones. Enjoy the open floor plan showcasing the lodge style furnishings, stone fireplaces, knotty pine open beamed cathedral ceilings, hardwood floors, and the most amazing views of Big Bear Lake!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Three levels of spacious sun decks wrap the property overlooking Big Bear Lake, making for the ideal place to relax against the great outdoors and socialize together under the eagle-perch pines. You&amp;#39;ll love soaking your muscles in the private 8-person spa on the lower deck as you take in the view plus a private boat dock is available in the warmer summer months. Bear Lake Lodge is a spectacular custom home, perfect for any occasion to the mountains, and ready for your next Big Bear vacation!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
