&lt;strong&gt;Crystal Pines at Big Bear Lake | Walk to Boulder Bay Park | Family-Friendly Retreat&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Discover the perfect Big Bear getaway at Crystal Pines, a beautifully upgraded mountain retreat just a short walk to Boulder Bay, lake access, kayaking, fishing, and scenic shoreline trails. Located on Waterview Dr.one of Boulder Bay&amp;rsquo;s most peaceful and desirable pockets this three-bedroom, two-bath home is designed for relaxation, adventure, and unforgettable mountain memories.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step into soaring ceilings, warm wood finishes, and two stunning stone fireplaces that create the ultimate cozy atmosphere after a day on the lake or the slopes. The expansive wraparound deck offers treetop views and a charming peek-a-boo look at Big Bear Lake, giving you the perfect setting for morning coffee, evening cocktails, or stargazing under the pines.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Inside, the open-concept layout is ideal for families and groups. The spacious living room flows seamlessly into the dining area and fully equipped kitchen, making it easy to cook, gather, and connect. All bedrooms are thoughtfully decorated with a modern mountain feel, and the bonus room above the garage provides extra space for kids, teens, game nights, or remote work.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy a fully fenced yard, a rare feature in Big Bear, offering privacy and a safe place for children or pets to play. Parking is easy with a two-car garage and additional driveway space, giving you stress-free access year-round.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
With its walkable location near the lake and its quick drive to The Village, hiking trails, Boulder Bay Park, Pleasure Point Marina, and ski resorts, Crystal Pines gives you everything you need for a year-round adventure, whether you&amp;#39;re here to ski, boat, hike, or unwind.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Book your stay and experience the comfort, charm, and convenience that make Crystal Pines the perfect home base for your Big Bear escape.&lt;br /&gt;
